{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_09_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマス前のある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nおやつは五百円以上買っても、いい？",
      "startTime": 3.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お、おやつ？\n一体なんの話を……あぁ、もしかして",
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "木組みの街でやる『ぱじゃパ！』のクリスマスライブに\n持って行くおやつが、なかなか決まらなくて",
      "startTime": 17.8117008369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "星見市と友好都市になった、木組みの街か\n……って、おやつを買う店ならあっちにもあるだろ？",
      "startTime": 25.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "星見市でしか買えないおやつを持って行けば\n木組みの街の人との、交流のきっかけになるかも……",
      "startTime": 32.9265316169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら五百円とは言わずに\nいろいろ買って行ってもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 40.2708393733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……！　確かに……。そうする\nネットで、木組みの街を調べたんだけど……",
      "startTime": 46.8647857826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく可愛くて、綺麗な街……実際に歩くのが楽しみ\nそれに、ライブ衣装のデザインも良かった",
      "startTime": 57.1314524492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "木組みの街のクリスマスにぴったりの可愛さ\nみんながあの衣装を着て歌って踊るのが楽しみ……！",
      "startTime": 65.4314524492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、雫も着て歌って踊るだろう？",
      "startTime": 70.028776765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "うん。『ぱじゃパ！』のみんなを観るのも\n自分が歌って踊るのも、楽しみ",
      "startTime": 76.8394796055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、どんなおやつを持って行くのかは\nもう考えてあるのか？",
      "startTime": 83.3375060399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんおすすめの、魚魚っとさんクッキーと\nそれから、魚魚っとさん饅頭……あと、何にしようかな",
      "startTime": 89.5979818663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさん？　星見市のマスコットではあるが……\nこのままだと、魚魚っとさん尽くしになりそうだな……",
      "startTime": 100.6041645686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――木組みの街から帰ってきた翌日",
      "startTime": 105.4578599773,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2189.524348500001,
          "startTime": 107.6473843258
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.2911897503
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.2911897503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん。お疲れ様、です\n質問があるんだけど、いい？",
      "startTime": 113.514047432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "雫？　今日はオフだったよな\nわざわざ事務所に来るなんて、どうかしたのか？",
      "startTime": 119.5375060399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.2366726322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに聞きたいことがあって\n事務所に寄った。いてくれて良かった",
      "startTime": 125.6762957256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ココアちゃん達に、星見市がどんな所か聞かれたから\n写真を送りたくて……データじゃない、現像したやつ",
      "startTime": 133.8763023377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.539581307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "寮の住所で出していい？　それとも、お仕事で\n出会ったから、事務所の住所で出した方が、いい？",
      "startTime": 142.6096361797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ココアさん……あぁ、木組みの街でお世話になった\nカフェの店員さん達か。手紙は寮の住所でいいよ",
      "startTime": 151.4708393733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.137338138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "本当？　良かった……\nお友達になったから……えへへ",
      "startTime": 158.9092503231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.5899456426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "宿の件もだが、ライブにもゲスト出演してもらったしな\n『ぱじゃパ！』のみんながお世話になった人達か……",
      "startTime": 167.2708393733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "でも俺はずっと仕事だったから、よく知らないんだ\nどんなことがあったのか、教えてもらえるか？",
      "startTime": 174.6375060399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.4845968966
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.4845968966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね、私達はラビットハウスっていう\n喫茶店の店員さんとして、お店のお手伝いをした",
      "startTime": 185.0872349104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse",
      "startTime": 190.6909909331
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse",
      "startTime": 190.6909909331
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse",
      "startTime": 190.9409909331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "制服も、貸してもらったんだ\nライブでも途中で着替えた、あの可愛い服",
      "startTime": 195.2539015771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あの制服、よく似合っていたよ\n喫茶店の仕事は難しくなかったか？",
      "startTime": 202.4375060399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse",
      "startTime": 205.1537804368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "ココアちゃん達がフォローしてくれてたから\nなんとかなった……！",
      "startTime": 208.0590719541,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3176.18668099999,
          "startTime": 211.2352586351
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi",
      "startTime": 210.6019232275
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi",
      "startTime": 210.6019232275
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "途中で、すずちゃんと買い出しに出掛けて\n木組みの街を歩いてみたんだけど……",
      "startTime": 215.3257386208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_09_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "知らない街だからか、少し迷っちゃって\nでも、街の人達が親切で、道を教えてもらった",
      "startTime": 222.3257386208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi",
      "startTime": 227.7748839142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
